<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Whispers of Light — A Photography Journey by Steve McCurry</h1>
    <p>Capturing the world’s untold stories through light, color, and soul — every image is a window into humanity.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About the Photographer</h2>
    <p>Steve McCurry is one of the most iconic voices in contemporary photography. Known for his evocative color images, he captures the human condition across cultures and landscapes. His work reflects compassion and curiosity, blending photojournalism with fine art storytelling.</p>
    <p>This showcase celebrates the art of seeing — finding beauty and meaning in fleeting moments of life around the globe.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="extended">
    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p><em>“Whispers of Light”</em> is a curated gallery inspired by the storytelling vision of Steve McCurry. It highlights the interplay of light and emotion — a visual exploration of humanity’s shared experiences across places and cultures. Each image is carefully chosen to represent the connection between people, place, and time.</p>
    <p>This project embodies the belief that photography transcends language — that every photograph can whisper a truth of its own.</p>
  </section>

